locality: East bank of Sangha River 45 km South of Lidjombo, from NDAKAN camp to 2 km South, riparian forest with Uapaca heudelotii and Irvingia smithii. Precp. 1400 mm.
Parc Nouabalé-Ndoki, Goualougo: 40 Km E-SE de Bomassa.
Ile M'Bamou, sous-bois en terre ferme, partie Moutou ya N 'Gombé.
Embouchure de la Nkunde derrière la plaine d'aviation. Ndjili-Kinshasa
